00:20:53.290 --> 00:20:55.940
Captain Yami always takes an extremely 
long time in the bathroom.

00:20:56.380 --> 00:20:57.520
So basically...

00:20:57.520 --> 00:20:59.660
None of them are normal.

00:20:59.660 --> 00:21:03.740
Wait, wait, wait! What kind of curse 
makes you stay in the bathroom forever?

00:21:03.740 --> 00:21:08.400
And if we're gonna get into it, everyone 
here is pretty undoubtedly unique, too!

00:21:08.400 --> 00:21:09.200
What?

00:21:09.200 --> 00:21:12.410
B-Being called unique is too embarrassing!

00:21:12.410 --> 00:21:14.230
Huh? Bone!

00:21:14.500 --> 00:21:15.900
But I'm completely normal.

00:21:15.900 --> 00:21:16.900
At any rate,

00:21:16.900 --> 00:21:20.050
you're the last one I want to hear 
that from, you zero-magic meathead!

00:21:23.290 --> 00:21:25.130
Oh, speaking of magic,

00:21:25.130 --> 00:21:28.770
maybe this is reacting to Henry.

00:21:28.770 --> 00:21:32.180
Oh, yeah. I guess his condition that 
sucks away everyone else's mana

00:21:32.180 --> 00:21:33.810
could definitely be a curse.

00:21:33.810 --> 00:21:35.130
Yeah, he's cursed.

00:21:35.130 --> 00:21:36.850
Indeed, he is.

00:21:37.330 --> 00:21:40.480
There's a huge flame in 
the royal capital, as well.

00:21:40.950 --> 00:21:44.330
I can't tell who exactly is cursed,

00:21:44.330 --> 00:21:47.490
but if you include the smaller 
flames, that's quite a few.

00:21:48.340 --> 00:21:50.330
Can't we get a look at a bigger area?

00:21:50.330 --> 00:21:53.490
If we go too far out, the accuracy falls.

00:21:56.500 --> 00:21:57.450
That's...

00:21:57.450 --> 00:21:59.040
The Heart Kingdom...

00:21:59.770 --> 00:22:02.050
And there's a very big flame coming from there.

00:22:03.500 --> 00:22:07.250
Maybe there's a clue about the devil there!

00:23:39.570 --> 00:23:41.480
You're my dad, Nathan.

00:23:41.480 --> 00:23:43.070
We found some clues 
on devils because of you.

00:23:43.070 --> 00:23:45.290
Thanks, Dad-Who's-Also-Nathan!

00:23:45.290 --> 00:23:47.640
My best friends are really happy, too!

